quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  67,15,Neupeujeuet bumoe keu tanyoe mudah Beudoh jak laju jeuet lungkiek bumoe Raseuki teuh nyoe sinan Neukeubah Tapajoh laju raseuki gata Dudoe tagisa tawoe bak Allah
  67,16,Ek aman gata bak ureueng langet Neuyue peusinget bumoe le Allah Meuguncang-guncang bumoe ngon gata
  67,17,Ek aman gata lom cuba peugah Batee Neuyue rhom bak ureueng langet ‘Oh keunong teupat mate teuh reubah Tateupue treuk peue nyang Lon peuingat Pakri saket that hanaban peugah
  67,18,Meunan pih kawom dilee nibak jih Han jitem pateh peue nyang peurintah Peue nyang geupeugah jikheun nyan sulet Pakriban saket keu jih Lon balah
  67,19,Peue hana jieu ticem teureubang Jipo lam awan rame jih leupah Meubareh-bareh jipo di ateuh Sayeup jipeulheuh jitop jipeuhah Tuhan nyang theun jih bek rhot u bumoe Neukalon dumpeue bandum le Allah
  67,20,Boh soe nyoe teuma nyang jeuet keu teuntra Nyang tulong gata ‘oh teuka musoh Meunyo kon Tuhan nyang that geumaseh Di kaphe paleh sabe lam salah Bandum si kaphe ka chetan taki
  67,21,Boh soe lom nyang bri bandum napakah Soe bri raseuki teuma keu gata Meunyo Neusangga Neutheun le Allah Tapi jeut mabok cit lom krang ceukang Batat ngon tungang dumpeue jibantah
  67,22,Ureueng jak meugom muka bak tanoh Soe got teuma jih ngon ureueng ceudah Geujak meusigak bak jalan teupat Soe nyang troh siat ho nyang geulangkah
  67,23,"Takheun Tuhan keuh nyang peujeuet gata Dilee phon mula sampoe ‘oh sudah Geulinyueng, mata ngon ate gata Bandum nyan nyata peuneujeuet Allah Tapi tachuko nit that nyang tatem"
  67,24,Takheun lom laen peuneujeuet Allah Neupeujeuet gata rame lam bumoe Meusapat dudoe teuma bak Allah
  67,25,Jitanyong pajan janji nyan teuka Meu beuna gata peue nyang tapeugah
  67,26,Takheun atra nyan ‘eleumee Tuhan Di lon nyoe mantong meu Neuyue peugah Neuyue peuingat bak lon nyoe mantong
  67,27,‘Oh ban jikalon azeub meurimbah Muka si kaphe bandum ka pucat Hana le ubat ka abeh sudah Geukheun lom bak jih nyoe nyang ka lakee Yoh masa dilee beu rijang leupah
  67,28,Takheun boh pakri meunyo lon mate Rakan lon sare pih abeh sudah Got pih di Tuhan Neugaseh kamoe Rahmat keu kamoe Neubri le Allah Soe nyang ek peuglah teuma si kaphe Azeub bukon le peudeh that leupah
  67,29,Takheun leh nyan keuh Tuhan nyang Rahman Kamoe meuiman bandum keu Allah Bandum bak Tuhan tawakai kamoe Tateupue dudoe soe nyang bit salah Soe nyang bit nyata jih nyan lam sisat
  67,30,Takheun leh siat pakri ‘oh susah Watee hana ie ka tho di bumoe Watee nyan bak soe teuma tapeugah Soe bri mata ie teuma keu gata Mangat dum gata tajep puleh grah